data.description: Maculatly maintained original owner home with spacious bedrooms, walk in clothes, open concept, huge backyard, and so much more! Entering the home through the beautiful, landscaped flower beds into the formal entry and formal dining on the right, half bath, kitchen, breakfast, and living room are all open and ready for entertaining for the holidays. The kitchen features walk in pantry, tons of cabinet and countertops, and new upgraded gas range. The fireplace will be the focus of the living room. Primary bedroom located on the first floor with his and her sinks, separate tub and shower, and the closet you have dreamed about. Upstairs you will find an open game room and three secondary bedrooms large enough for king beds and additional furniture. Don't miss this back yard! Covered patio for grilling and enjoying the outdoors with room to build a pool, playset, or large garden to go with the fruit trees that are planted in the back yard. This home offers a sprinkler system too!
